{"tid":1879921,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"抗爭者的情人節　17歲女友懲教所探望還柙男友　縱使觸不到也希望見一面2020/2/14 - 20:12","createTime":"2020-02-14T13:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T13:58:44.000Z","uid":77792,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"31cc7aa8eea4a453b6ebc7a9543aaee119bb2d20","tid":1879921,"uid":77792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:15:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n_uoWELuRLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn_uoWELuRLQ&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=6f7f6539\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n_uoWELuRLQ</a><br />\n<br />\n情人節街上一對對愛侶慶祝節日，17歲的 Yuko（化名）原也以為可以和男友甜密過節，豈料反送中運動，令二人被高牆分隔。今個情人節，在懲教所15分鐘的會面、一包袋裝朱古力便是他們僅有的接觸。<br />\n去年10月，Yuko 的男友因抗爭運動被捕，至今仍被還柙。Yuko表示知道他是前線抗爭者，雖然一直十分擔心，但仍然沒有過問，「佢只係話做嘅事都危險。我覺得，每個人都有自己的方法去表達自己對這個政權、社會環境嘅不滿。」<br />\n<br />\n「都預咗佢有一日可能真係會被捕，但當佢真的被人拉咗嘅時候。都有一瞬間去諗點解偏偏係佢。」Yuko 憶述收到電話得知男友被捕後腦海一片空白，她一直壓抑情緒，惟目睹男友提訊一刻，不禁潸然淚下，「他望到我嘅第一個反應係對着我笑， 佢係想我安心，你俾人審緊都仲對住我笑，我真係覺得佢好蠢。」<br />\n<br />\n還柙至今4個月，Yuko 每周都至少探望男友兩次，「花個幾鐘入去，但淨係見得佢15分鐘，我每次都唔想咁快完，但無辦法。」至於情人節，Yuko 說有早點起床打扮才出門到懲教所，又買了袋裝朱古力作禮物，雖然只是懲教處規定可交送的零食，但已是二人意義最重大的一分禮物，「上年佢有送玫瑰花畀我，亦都有喺屋企樓下傾計食糖水，今年情人節都沒辦法掂到對方，但都希望可以見下對方。」<br />\n問到對男友的情人節祝福，Yuko 思索良久才回答道：「我只想佢知道我會一直陪佢，只想佢開心、平安，咁就夠。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e8c2cd54bb2539b45704bf64f63db27cc1f7fb","tid":1879921,"uid":77792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:17:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"947b8cba597c1904c11156a1a1c711699948073e","tid":1879921,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1eb804ede40c555dfa99f4230dc55f6e41025a8","tid":1879921,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556058307fe019890092f8d8450bbc770ba8fa99","tid":1879921,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a7dc01302fb004bee4c6c4d55d148d3ead81f9","tid":1879921,"uid":45450,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:27:23.000Z","msg":"踏入後反送中浪漫主義時代？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c75c9a974b1454b8559528a7fe7b0256625863e","tid":1879921,"uid":2577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea971ebcc935c5dff26600b0663c588984120e65","tid":1879921,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"無謂吖 連登仔唔會幫你 最多留個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算"},{"pid":"99277668f3de18ef64187671268acbd0e48f67b9","tid":1879921,"uid":191762,"like"